Class Application

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.ws.rs.core.Application
      • com.atomgraph.core.Application
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Application

    public class Application
extends javax.ws.rs.core.Application
implements Application
    AtomGraph Core JAX-RS application base class. Can be extended or used as it is (needs to be configured in web.xml). Needs to register JAX-RS root resource classes and providers.
    Author:
    Martynas Juseviƒçius <martynas@atomgraph.com>
